{"tid":875884,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞][原曲：Faded] 講普通話～","createTime":"2018-10-25T08:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T01:34:49.000Z","uid":108844,"like":60,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0f41d64a1ab9be49869eab2f2bb2322eba2860","tid":875884,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"原曲：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/60ItHLz5WEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F60ItHLz5WEA&d=m%2F180F9IkiAbVluShB6ehwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=742bcf82\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/60ItHLz5WEA</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n國語是每日要說的 哪個唔識<br />\n你再去避 實被嫌棄<br />\n國語是上學會教的 誰人都掂<br />\n快點<br />\n<br />\n講普通話～波Paul麼科～<br />\n講普通話～教會歌都不須再怕<br />\n講普通話～你我也已經被大陸化<br />\n<br />\n講普通話～說實情<br />\n來港的事 全家都是<br />\n舉家搬遷～有綜援騙～<br />\n不斷輸入一直不斷行劫<br />\n毛語錄 全要讀<br />\n貴族 攜英鎊 離了港<br />\n快做 人工島<br />\n<br />\n國庫要抗衡特朗普 冇哂糧草<br />\n要靠稅務 慢慢填數<br />\n你有錢拿來建個島 唔洗問<br />\n靠搶<br />\n<br />\n講普通話～玩抖音啦～<br />\n唔多識字 繁體不易<br />\n唔知點搵 女廁<br />\n如忍不住 來找棵樹<br />\n<br />\n踎低屙屎～臭味濃<br />\n來港的事 全家都是<br />\n踎低屙屎～你要留意～<br />\n忍讓體諒請別阻住如廁<br />\n毛語錄 全要讀<br />\n貴族 攜英鎊 離了港<br />\n快做 人工島"},{"pid":"56d1f57f9838c310680c81494d724eeb985c6cfd","tid":875884,"uid":108844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"寫到最後覺得好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb59ddd2ebaeccdc4c918acfc7f5fafb1db9c24","tid":875884,"uid":26878,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:03:18.000Z","msg":"龜龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a02f14b4b3cc671bc59436dc70e70161212347e","tid":875884,"uid":108844,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"efb59ddd2ebaeccdc4c918acfc7f5fafb1db9c24","tid":875884,"uid":26878,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018